{"tid":1507641,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔係打J，抗爭真係勝利在望","createTime":"2019-08-26T08:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T09:50:30.000Z","uid":281193,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2398242f1ae5b218c31936c2858871c961cbaf53","tid":1507641,"uid":281193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"呢兩日勇武嘅手足升咗幾個呢<br />\n因為前線已經唔怕死，帶住一份堅定不怯嘅心態落場<br />\n<br />\n相反，狗，睇得出當佢地對住生死相摶，真係會怯<br />\n<br />\n狗，只係打工，為份厚糧，有家庭，佢地怕永久傷殘，佢地怕冇命<br />\n所以，佢地怯。<br />\n<br />\n佢地失去理智開槍，代表佢地內心係好怯<br />\n<br />\n當越來越多狗知道落場係會冇命、係會永久傷殘<br />\n<br />\n佢地一定會將壓力俾高層同政府，拒絕落場做棋子。<br />\n<br />\n我咁講，唔係繼續推手足去死，一方面向義士致敬，祝佢地平平安安<br />\n二方面只係想指出狗心已經虛怯。"},{"pid":"a07c33c103c763019af03ffb0e267a1998936103","tid":1507641,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=deb7efb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"46aefadc1614573b4becf36c7a3d95a3a9f2f486","tid":1507641,"uid":147366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a07c33c103c763019af03ffb0e267a1998936103","tid":1507641,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=deb7efb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_bl